{"tid":1505142,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"推到佢收皮，東亞銀行中大分行bm Andy Shek","createTime":"2019-08-25T12:57:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T16:00:05.000Z","uid":297603,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"b9a825738d5783f3a63a303a805d449481f5e4c3","tid":1505142,"uid":297603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:57:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vsjS1eA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvsjS1eA.jpg&h=17e68cb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作為金融能都覺得好羞恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一齊送9佢一程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nBwqBOt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnBwqBOt.jpg&h=13292bf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先生／小姐台鑒  :<br />\n     本人對 東亞銀行香港中文大學分行旗下職員 Andy Shek於八月二十五日在facebook上發佈的兩則惡意貼文：「非常非常非常支持嚴懲搞不合作運動既所有示威者 不X知所謂 成班都死不足惜」以及「曱甴 應該被消滅 應該被清算」作出強烈譴責，認為完全不能接受。<br />\n該名分行職員在網上肆意留下惡質、企圖對他人身體作出傷害的攻擊性以及恐嚇留言，讓本人感到極之恐慌，亦不敢前往其所屬分行辦理財務。本人認為旗下職員 Andy Shek絕對嚴重地損害了東亞銀行素來予人友善待客的印象，破壞了貴行悠存已久之良好聲譽。本人認為東亞銀行應對該名職員員作出解僱或予以適當處分，確保客人在銀行不會面對人身安全的恐嚇。<br />\n故特來函 貴行申訴。敬希 能盡快給本人合理的回覆。<br />\n<br />\n順祝<br />\n近安<br />\n<br />\n                                                   投訴人<br />\n<br />\n                                                               XXX<br />\n2019年8月25日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去呢個網submit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkbea.com/cgi-bin/bea-enquiry-form.jsp?language=tc&amp;stepId=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkbea.com%2Fcgi-bin%2Fbea-enquiry-form.jsp%3Flanguage%3Dtc%26stepId%3D1&d=06o7JzqVhDqA6Aam%2BaIp86VJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=b384f1cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkbea.com/cgi-bin/bea-enquiry-form.jsp?language=tc&amp;stepId=1</a>"},{"pid":"3a8dc6737bb061c99dd74379aa93160b505e0983","tid":1505142,"uid":209464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:28:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"682eb9b82bc9bda6ee94ab2df9d88c2fdfeddf91","tid":1505142,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:29:05.000Z","msg":"想出名一定幫佢 推！"},{"pid":"92e3f8c01fb48c214c98a84c1442bb57596982f2","tid":1505142,"uid":1212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:32:09.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"a0e479602baa0e1bbd85c626942a47ea14a47c0e","tid":1505142,"uid":255222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:36:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3e37145476fdda9d2db24b211854fb7aba5bbf6b","tid":1505142,"uid":255222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:02:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e305177f5d04dd1515ddf82869d3d014bf1e65a6","tid":1505142,"uid":169579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T01:06:10.000Z","msg":"十連推 一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c1b0c20a98e93702e99d5fb67c935e1494154d7","tid":1505142,"uid":169579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T01:06:49.000Z","msg":"十連推二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3190de81a70fbba04f71d7b79deffb33beb8dac5","tid":1505142,"uid":169579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply